Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天不是還要去做家教嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總得先休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能來看正式演出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是排練
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說錯了是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做事的原則是邊探討邊推進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排練也應該以這種方式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都這麼覺得  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了  就是沒幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你搞的這些誇張的玩意兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是上一輩的嬉皮士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是說過設計按照畫的樣子來就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是參考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你居然原封不動地做出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導演的風格最近一直都在變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跟著我們的步調來商量怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種畫太幼稚  根本看不懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之改改吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  幸虧公演不是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又不想去  夕風的學祭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去見由綺也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎  我前兩天又…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白癡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了  我做什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間不夠時就要用人海戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤倉小姐是指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和這個廢物該做些什麼  請下令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座敷童子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是座敷童子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在問由綺你的哥哥回來了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺是那位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝這邊看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  時間差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不唱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新曲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱首新曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒練習多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為補償  有一件事要告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸  美笑她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來打算叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但澤倉小姐說  就讓你睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你參加展銷會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼展銷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出節目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮演布朗神父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得嗎  布朗寧詩集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從美笑那裏借來的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  福爾摩斯的助手…對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願上帝保佑你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道美笑在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你說的是要加敬稱的那個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  Happys來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人嚇了一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  風頭全被搶過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有人氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…由綺  森川由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對對  由綺醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小八
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小響
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  能不能別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊抱歉  可以不要拍照嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺她…來了這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六你準備做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在學校裏轉轉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有認真地在排練了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上我們做的那些衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真地在做了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君說話的方式好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是正式的排練嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑沒來看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  收拾好就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  都沒怎麼睡過嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  多虧了你們睡得很香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定要來看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好的印在眼裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然見外起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你父親都過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天結束後會去感謝  順便打掃下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩幫我轉告他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了呢…終於
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了  應該不會再有這樣的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  再有這樣的事隨時可以找我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在忙嗎  那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已經做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了錯了  那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計是…不會滿座的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那邊的佈景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開場後演員入場時怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點拆掉  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最靠後的角落裏就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人的位置都不能想想辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒睡醒嗎  美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾席是為觀眾而存在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也算是個工作人員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然總是在需要你的時候不見人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去邊上看吧  不許搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不可能堅持到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好心到通宵幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好心幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你沒問題哦  自己去觀眾席上看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,票到接待處去買  成人票700日元一張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田丸  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑  我去買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跟你廢話了  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上要開演了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦美笑  我去買票…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！不能聽任田丸擺佈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我去買了後把票給美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就誰也不能多嘴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那藤井君怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天也稍微看了點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天就不必特意再看了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意跟我一起看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就買兩張  弄兩個位子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好想想  田丸不允許我坐在觀眾席
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也不會賣你兩張的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就請跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑  那難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二樓的坐席現在沒有開放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看台被當成了雜物房
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年準備學祭的時候被叫去拿腰鼓的時候發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最裏面的牆後  有照明用的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏的話  就不會被人打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首鈴  還有5分鐘就開演了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大探險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  之後只要直走就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  終點近在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,序章只能放棄了  田丸的獨演要持續一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天看了哦  好像時代劇一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時代劇？我好像要發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  既然決定了  就稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.27,0:16:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝  我正好口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人懷念啊  這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎  日川町的那個電影院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三映館？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  正好就是這種氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光束下  飄著煙塵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們碰見過吧  美笑一個人去那的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  藤井君是跟由綺一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺那傢伙  一看到美笑就跑過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人一起親親熱熱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我挺嫉妒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是被她纏著  熱得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候明明也是冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  還能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟美笑一起  看到各種各樣的美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你看到了很多弱點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡的學姐  而且偶爾成為只屬於我的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很尊敬你  跟由綺一樣想永遠跟著你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  彰不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彰對美笑的心意跟我們不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然說起這個來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑  你對彰怎麼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是現在該說的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  誰在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑對不起  我竟然說出這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當心那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏痛？腳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  太黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭到了嗎  要是骨折就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我馬上去叫救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  留在這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  留在這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我說那麼奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  早就決定好了…變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美…笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四幕  骯髒而邪惡的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起因是詩集  演劇劇本  設計
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤解  妄想不斷膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒學弟的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至嫉妒她的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛她  欺騙她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道學弟的朋友的心意  卻不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑  不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:19:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把學弟…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別回答我的告白  因為你有由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你根本沒想過我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你放心吧  錯的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒發現嗎  這都是我安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能讓我的劇本登上舞台而利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骯髒而邪惡的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的只有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  耽誤了你的時間  你可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑  我喜歡你  很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡你  所以你走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  那呆子在那種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑  …
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終幕  接受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十頁  獨角戲之所以空虛  並非因為只有一個演員
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.00,0:24:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是觀眾的目光  刺得好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.35,0:24:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album

